ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"我真心不問世事<br />\n所以咩都唔關我事"},{"pid":"572ac549c3620e5a120112847bb40be09b06e207","tid":1634281,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"唔撚理政治<br />\n第日送中<br />\n警察入你屋企強姦你老婆 個女 唔好上黎後後侮"},{"pid":"26b7a501407d1dbdba7738c347262510f3e69ae1","tid":1634281,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bf0e75f5c859084c4d6e4014c57ad59e91f5648","tid":1634281,"uid":115638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6806a17f54b153d0dc3cf574b712ce470993758","tid":1634281,"uid":174322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:17:52.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲嗰頭扮不問世事<br />\n依頭爛幅玻璃都嘈到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知以為間嘢佢地有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"我真心不問世事<br />\n所以咩都唔關我事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"嗰頭見到咩事都啞撚咗咁，做沉默大多數<br />\n依頭爛部閘機都屌鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心你啞嘅就啞落去啦<br />\n衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af033eb94c709f6fe13e38e7757275722fce0c35","tid":1634281,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"而家搞到出蒙面法咪關事囉, 病咗唔比戴口罩傳埋比家人朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de195bc712b14a267de1679ebda46c99008913d7","tid":1634281,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"572ac549c3620e5a12011284